This vagrant project prepares three nodes for running corosync cluster.

It prepares cluster up to section 2.5.3

You can continue execution of commands from the Cluster from the scratch guide starting from the section 2.5.3

The nodes' names are node-1, node-2, node-3

Ssh keys are installed on the nodes and allow passwordless access.

Httpd and wget are installed. index.html is prepopulated you just have to updated it with node numbers.

DRDB packages are already installed.

Instead of adding a logical volume we create /dev/sdb

Install drbd on node 1 and 2 only.
Before you configure drbd on every node run this:
$ hostname node-<number>
